  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="257212451">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-257212451" class="vote-count">2</span>
              <a id="btn-257212451" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="257212451">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1129320/">koala</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/257212451">2010-07-25 19:38:24</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">在库斯马库斯拉大街，真是北京的。前面有些精致的淘气，让人会心一笑，非常喜欢“有不爱吃胡萝卜的小孩”那篇，太美好了。后面多是水，是质量不高的博客，也许，是我平时所看的博客质量都太高了？</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/3225748/?comment_id=257212451"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="990568824">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-990568824" class="vote-count">21</span>
              <a id="btn-990568824" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="990568824">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/eiris/">砚小朵™</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/990568824">2015-12-23 23:14:23</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">一本神奇的书，明明是论坛灌水般的散扯，却有孤独的自得其乐，精致的淘气，会被狠狠地萌到。我记得那是2004年，我混天涯博客，勉强算个网红，而饭饭的博客更是大神级别的红。这个毕业于北大历史系叫黄国弋的女孩，有一把游弋性灵的文字。十年后，这个人消失匿迹了，她远遁于微博时代，过着不为人知的编辑生活。红是暂时，而生活是永恒。饭饭没有生在微博时代，会可惜吗？</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/3225748/?comment_id=990568824"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
